inn1.comm: lands the first delivery on a length, gets it to move from Salman Butt who punches it well but straight to covers
drifts on to the legs, whipped hard but straight to square leg. Salman is looking to very confident here. Two well-timed strokes though he is yet to find the gaps
on the middle and leg, moving towards middle, defended to the on side
a tad slower, 121.1 kmph delivery just outside off, Salman was early into his punch-drive and almost dragged it back into his leg stump.
gets forward to get in line of a length delivery that straightens outside off and steers it to third man
leans forward to defend a delivery around the off stump.
full delivery around the off stump, pushed to the off side
on a length, just outside off stump, good bounce, pushed to cover point
full pitched, well outside off stump and Salman drives through extra cover. He went down on his knee and powered it off his bottom hand
drags back the length, tightens the line to just outside off and is defended to the off side
on the off and middle line, straightens a touch, pushed to point
gets forward to punch a full length delivery back to Ishant.
leans forward to defend

shout for lbw but turned down. It came in from the middle and off and caught Akmal on the shuffle. It would have hit the top of the stumps. Aamir Sohail, on air, thought there might be an inside edge but the tv replays don't show it. Anyway the umpire must have thought it would have gone over. It hit the sticks right on top.
leans forward to push the delivery to the on side
drives well but Raina dives to his left at covers to make the stop
down leg and brushes the pad, bounces before it reaches Dhoni
just outside off stump and mistimes a drive to the off side
back of the length, outside off stump and Salman forces it to wide third man
top edged over Dhoni. Surprise bouncer and Akmal is late on the pull.

cuts in from just outside off stump, Akmal stabs it off the inside edge and on to the pad. Akmal turns around in a hurry as he fears the ball might run on to the stumps but it just sits there near his foot and winks at him. You get the idea...
just outside off stump, cutting in, pushed to the off side.
just outside the off stump, punched to mid-off. I fear Ishant's body might just tear apart the release. Full effort at the release.
another nagging in cutter and Akmal gives respect
leans forward to drive to mid-off
leans forward to punch a delivery to mid-on
just outside off stump, moving away, Butt tries to bottom-hand it through the off side and gets an inside edge to fine leg.
hint of inswing, on the off and middle, pushed back down the track
slower one, on the legs, turned to square leg
nip backer on the off stump, pushed to covers
on a length, just outside off stump - the nagging line and length continues, mistimes another bottom-handed drive to the off side.
hits the deck short of length but spears it into the hips, Butt twists his body quickly to put bat to ball and gets a single down to fine leg
kicks up from short of length, straightens, Akmal is almost squared-up  as he wanted to hit to midwicket and adjusts to push it out to the off side
slower one, around 115 kmph delivery, breaks in from outside off stump - delivered with an off break action, defended to the off side
lands outside off stump, cuts in a touch, pushed to covers
Shot yaar! Short of length and width outside off stump, Akmal stood up on his toes, got on top of the bounce nicely and cut it through point. Good horizontal-bat stroke.
punches a length delivery to short straight mid-off where Sehwag makes the stop
on the middle and leg, off a length, wristed to fine leg
fuller, shaping in towards middle, Akmal drives to mid-off
and back to the bowler now. Pakistan have made a cautious start in overcast conditions. They don't want to lose any early wickets
straightens after landing on a length around off, opens the bat-face and guides to third man
moving across Salman who stays on the leg stump line and punches it wide mid-off
starts off with a poor delivery- short and wide and Salman crashes it to the point boundary. What the tv comms would have said, disappeared like a tracer bullet. A
straighter, turned to the on side,
just outside off stump, opens the bat-face and guides to point
back of length, cut to point
waits for the ball to come to him before steering it to right of third man
slower one, driven to short mid-off where Sehwag fields
mistimes a length delivery to covers. Praveen Kumar has been constantly varying his pace and the batsmen have been unable to find the right timing
driven to Sehwag who back flicks a throw at the non-striker's end and Akmal gets back in time.
fuller, on the middle and leg, wristed past square leg
Salman Butt stands just outside the crease and mistimes a cut to the off side. Again too much bottom-hand and going too hard at it.
another mistimed stroke, a pull this time and he will get a single behind square leg. The wicket should get slower as the game progresses
yet another mistimed drive, a single to left of mid-off.
Shot boss! he walked across the stumps and pulled a length delivery over midwicket. Predetermined but effective this time.

He is gone now. Again, he walked across the stumps, Irfan alert this time hurled it full and outside off and Akmal edged a drive low to the right of Dhoni who makes no mistake. Something had to give as the runs weren't coming thick and fast.
what a fab shot to get off the mark. And he raises his bat to the crowd! ha! Lovely extra cover drive. Everything right about the stroke,. the feet, the head and the timing.
well outside off stump, steered to third man
short of length, pushed to mid-on
on a length, angling into the batsman, defended off the front foot
short ball, outside off, Younis tries to hook that, doesn't get hold of it, fielded at midwicket
good length, jabbed towards mid-on, batsmen go through for a quick single, fielder failed to pick up the ball, could have been right
good, tight bowling from Praveen, Butt defends it back to the bowler
hit to cover point, no run
Dropped short and a bit of width, Butt unleashes a fierce cut, went low to Rohit Sharma's right at cover point but couldn't hold on to a difficult chance. Praveen isn't too happy with that effort
driven crisply  through the covers, boundary,  Younis is off to a good start here
no room being allowed for the batsman, Younis defends
good length, in the channel, defended by Younis
again just outside off, Younis backs away and punches it square, but straight to the fielder
full delivery, maintain a nagging line, Younis gets on the front foot and pats it back to the bowler
another dot ball, defended to the off, good comeback by Irfan after that first ball went for four
shortish delivery, in the channel, Butt defends
given some room to free his arms, Butt is very strong square of the wicket, he cuts it for a single
back of a length, defended confidently by Younis
overpitched, a bit outside off, Younis gets on the front foot and drives it down the ground, doesn't beat a straightish mid-off though
slower delivery, beats Younis' attempt to glide it fine, pitches again before reaching the keeper
a bit short, and some width, Younis crashes that but superbly stopped by Raina in the covers
short, some width and Butt easily guides that to third man for a single
pushed to mid-on
length delivery, just outside off, Butt tickles it fine, and a squarish third man can't get to that
consecutive boundaries for Butt, short and outside off, pulled through midwicket
full, slower ball, adjusts at the last minute to push it to mid-off
good length, holds it line outside off, Butt tries to drive it but is beaten
jags into Younis, pushedto mid-on for a single
full and wide, angling across the batsman, Butt slashes at that but doesn't connect
short of a length, on the backfoot, jabbed to covers
another dot ball, pushed towards mid-off
full, slower delivery on the stumps, Butt adjusts and defends it back to the bowler
Butt gets some width this time, no footwork, tries to force it through the covers, but can't
overpitched delivery, a lot of width outside off, Younis gets on the front foot and his attempted drive takes a thick outside edge and races to third man
strays onto his pads, Butt turns it square on the leg side
another wide full delivery to Younis, he reaches for that, another edge and more work for third man
good length, middle-stump line, Butt gets another comfortable single pushing it to midwicket
better delivery to Younis, no width at al, full and Younis defends it confidently
short of a length, on off, Younis gets on the back foot and clips it towards midwicket for another single
short and wide, Younis gets on the back foot and crunches that, but his placement isn't too good, and it is fielded by Yuvraj at cover point
full and on leg, Younis pushes it to mid-on, straight to Yusuf Pathan, Butt was backing up pretty far at the non-striker's end, could have been tight if Yusuf had hit
short and on off, Yousuf defends off the back foot
Ishant's maintaining a good line, this one was back of a length, defended to the leg side
very full, drifting down leg, and a leg bye is taken. First extra of the innings
back of a length, on leg stump, Butt turns it to square leg for a single
well flighted delivery, fullish on middle, hit to midwicket
starys on the leg, swept away behind square for a couple
flighted again, Butt turns it to leg but can't beat short midwicket
better line, on a length turns in from outside off, turned past square leg
Chawla's getting a bit of turn, that pitched outside leg and came in, defended by younis
changes his line to outside off this time, again defended by Younis
length and on off, mistimed, bat turns in his hand as it trickles to mid-off
thick inside edge square on the leg
short of length, coming in, clipped past square leg
short and wide, Butt jabs it to the off
length ball on off, defended off the front foot
googly, on a length outside off, Butt spotted that and defends
flighted, overpitched on off, Butt launches that over the bowler's head
on leg, tries to sweep, was too early on that hits the back of his bat, but safe
flicked in front of square leg
swept for a couple where Brother Yo makes the stop
just outside off stump, Younis goes back to place it to cover point for a single
sharp spin and he is in trouble. It spun from outside off stump, Butt stabs it off the outside edge to the off side
turns this one to the on side
fuller, beats the waft and runs off the pad. Sehwag shouted for an lbw decision but it struck the batsman outside leg
just outside off stump, turning in, tickled to short third man
flighted delivery, driven back to Sehwag
turns in to Salman who pushes it back to Chawla
slower through the air, but on the leg and middle and swept away for a single
lands just outside off, breaks back in a touch, cut to backward point
fuller, bit more air and swept to Praveen Kumar at long leg
turns in from outside off stump, Butt waited before dabbing it late to right of short third man
leans forward to tickle a full delivery to short fine leg region
Younis breaks free with a six over long-on. He waltzed down the track, got to the pitch of the flighted delivery and swung it over the ropes
a tad short, flatter as well, cut to deep point
slower in the air, turns into Younis who works it to midwicket
spins in, turns it past square leg
on the middle and leg, pushed to long-on
square driven to left of Gambhir at deep point. Younis Khan comes back for the second but he didn't plant his bat inside the crease at the non-striker's end. One short, as they say.
flighted well outside off stump and driven to right of Gambhir at sweeper cover who fires in a direct hit at the non-striker's end and it ricochets away for an overthrow
turning past the off stump, turned to backward point
Mighty slog sweep against the turn. Some shot that. He went down on his knee to swing it high over deep midwicket
leans forward to push a flighted delivery outside off back to the bowler
lands outside off stump, turns away, YOunis tries to cut off the front foot and is beaten by the extra bounce
from round the stumps, floated on the middle, jabs it off the inside edge to the on side
a tad short, cut to covers
flighted delivery on the off, slog swept to deep midwicket.
leans forward to on drive a tossed-up delivery to long-on
drifts in with the arm, Butt manages to stab it away to the on side at the last minute
gets forward to drive to the right of the diving bowler down to long-off for a single
googly from outside leg stump, short too, lapped to long leg
leans forward to get to a low dipping full toss and swings it from well outside off to wide long-on. Younis is on the bike here
Wonderful placement. He thrust his front foot across and swept a flighted delivery from outside off to deep square leg boundary.
again stretches across and works a turning delivery outside off to wide midwicket
turns in to middle and off, tickled behind square leg for a single that brings up his ninth ODI fifty.
pushes a delivery on the off stump to covers
couple of steps down the track and wrists to long-on for a single
straight delivery on the off stump, nudged square on the off side for a single
Butt turns it on. He goes on his knee to heave a full delivery one bounce over midwicket
arm ball from round the stumps, dabbed to short third man
spinning away from the off stump, cut to covers where Yuvraj misfields
full, from round the stumps, turned through midwicket for a single and that's his 33rd ODI fifty. He started off with a boundary then plodded along but he has upped the ante in the recent overs.
swept past square leg for a single
rotates the strike with a dab
Salman rushes down the track and heaves a delivery turning into him over midwicket
on the off stump, pushed back to Yuvraj
leans across to wrist a on drive to long-on for another single
short and is cut hard but straight to Yuvraj at covers
well outside off, again short, cut to sweeper cover
Younis continues to make merry. What a turn around. Again short and he rocked back to pull it to wide long-on
and unfurls a reverse sweep now. Dhoni saw him about to play that short, moved to his right but Younis got the ball to the right of him for a single
pushes it down to long-on

Another boundary in that wide long-on region. Lovely placement. He took a couple of steps down the track, Raina dragged back the length but Younis adjusted to punch it over the infield and found the gap perfectly
the runs keep flooding in now. Tossed up well outside off stump and Salman stretches across to crash it to extra cover boundary where IShant makes a valiant attempt but can't get to it
pings the long-on for a run
drifts in with the arm, pushed through mid-on for a single.
on the off stump,nudged to backward point
quicker, fuller, driven to long-on
drifts in full, almost yorker length, driven to covers
he starts with the round-the-stumps attack, drifts it to on the hips, clipped behind square leg
lands it on a length, just outside off, straightens, defended to cover point
square drives a length delivery outside off on the up to wide third man
late cut ala Ranatunga. It was a back of length delivery outside off, coming in from round the stumps, he opened the bat -face and dabbed it fine
goes to the over-the-wickets line, lands it on a length on the off stump, punched to the off side
fuller, slower, misses the waft and it runs off the pad

short of length outside off and cut to right of deep point where Ishant makes the stop. Irfan suggests that Ishant should have released the ball earlier than he did. So does Yuvraj who signals to Ishant that he should have run faster
beaten on the cut outside off
cuts in a touch, around the off stump, punched to covers
edged to third man boundary. Short of length and well outside off, Salman slashes it off the outside edge.
fuller, closer to the off stump, worked to midwicket
on the middle, worked past square leg for a single
short of length, moving away from the off stump, punched to covers.
on the middle stump line, pushed back to the bowler. Younis has another chat with Salman
slower, fuller, on the middle, worked to deep midwicket
banged in short and Younis pulls it just over midwicket. He didn't time it well and will pick up couple of runs. He practices that shot again
length delivery outside off and Younis drives on the up but straight to covers
slower one outside off, short in length ,cut to right of Ishant who rushes across to make the stop and releases the ball quickly. Praveen Kumar applauds his effort.
works from outside off to the on side for a single
full and outside off, Salman thought about sweeping before pulling out of the stroke and jabbed it to the off side
flighted full outside off, driven to long-off
Younis fetches a legbreak from well outside off and top edged his slog sweep to the cow corner
short and cut to sweeper cover
low full toss, swept to long leg for a single
well outside off stump for the first wide of Pakistan's innings
fullish, just outside off stump, driven to sweeper cover
yorker length on the middle stump line, dug out towards mid-on for a single
full and outside off stump, driven to long-on
short of length delivery on the off and middle and Younis pulls it high in the air and it drops between long-on and deep midwicket.
just outside off stump, cut through point for couple of runs. Umpire Ashoka tells Salman, who ran right down the middle of the track for the second run, to get off the danger area
pulls a short of length delivery one bounce to Piyush at deep midwicket
flighted delivery outside off stump and Younis pings the wide long-on region again. He went down on his knee and another lovely slog sweep. Clean swing of the bat. 150 of the partnership up
cuts through point for a single
plays the sweep shot and Younis is back on the strike now
beaten by the leg break. Younis wanted to run it down to cover point region and the ball spun past the outside edge
cuts a googly to short third man
will retain the strike with a sweep to long leg
full one, driven to long-on
turning past the off stump, pushed to right of Sehwag who fumbles initially beofer recovering quickly
Super slog sweep again. That cowcorner is being peppered repeatedly by these two.
rotates the strike with a drive to long-off
really full one just outside off stump, Younis adjusts to the length by getting his bat down in a hurry and opening the bat-face to chop it past Irfan at short third man
You could have guessed it. Another slog sweep and the ball bisects deep midwicket and long-on perfectly. The white ball is disappearing here at Mirpur
outside off, tapped to the off side ,Younis wants a run, sent back by Salman
shout for lbw but a leg bye is given. He shuffled across, missed the sweep and was hit on the off stump. It would have drifted past the off
short delivery outside off, pulled to his favourite wide long-on region for couple of runs.
fuller, outside off again, Younis lunges across to work it to the on side
quciker, on the off stump, punched to covers
Piyush bowls a short turning delivery from round the stumps, lapped past square leg
googly outside off, cut to sweeper cover
turning outside off and Younis rocks back to cut to Ishant at deep cover

turns in to the middle stump, Salman flicks uppishly over midwicket and will come back for the second run and that's his 7th ODI hundred, fifth against India. He raises his bat before going down to the ground to offer sajda
on the off stump, pushed away
The ball is flying everywhere. This one is deposited over deep midwicket boundary. He went down on his knee, got under a short of length delivery and pulled it brutally
quicker delivery coming in from round the stumps, defended to tsshe off side
outside off, swept for a single
comes down the track, moving to the leg side in the process and drives to long-off
cut to sweeper cover for yet another single
really full in length, driven to long-on
flighted delivery outside off, driven to long-off
slower one outside off stump, Younis waits for it before punching it past the non-striker for a single. Irfan lunged across to his left, bumped into Salman and apologises
fullish, backs to the leg side, chops it through point
tries to jab a full one outside off to third man, misses and Dhoni gathers. Younis just one short of  the ton

Ad he gets there now. A hundred after two ducks. He is delirious. He took the helmet off as he ran for the single after punching the length delivery to long-off. He started the turn around, took the risks, played some big shots and changed the momentum of the innings.
another single, they have been taking the singles on every opportunity

dropped by Yusuf Pathan. Younis had lofted a full delivery and Yusuf ran in from long-on and dived full length but couldn't get his palms under it. And Rameez Raja, on air, says, "Had he taken it , it would have been the catch of the millenium!" Now then now then!
above waist-high full toss, pulled to deep backward square leg boundary
another full toss, not above waist-high though, outside off, Younis fails to connect with his square drive.
beaten again this time by a slower one. Full and just outside off, Younis walked into his checked-drive and the ball went past the outside edge

another waist-high full toss, lapped to short fine leg and they pick up a over throw as well. Oh the umpire doesn't think it was above waist high but replays do show that it was above that height. Hmm...
hello! another full toss, just below waist I guess, swatted to midwicket region
moves outside leg to push a full delivery through cover point
done in by the slower one. Younis was early into his lofted drive and lobs it to Sehwag at midwicket. But it was a fab innings from Younis Khan; he has propelled Pakistan towards a strong total.
full and on the middle stump line, Misbah sweeps it past square leg
googly outside off, full, driven hard to long-off
slider on the off and middle, defended to the off side
leans forward to tap a legbreak to the off side, looks for a single but Piyush rushes across to kill that thought
When in doubt, slog sweep. Misbah fetched it from well outside off and swept to wide midwicket region
And when you have no doubt, reverse sweep. Misbah gets it past the short third man fielder
straightens it off a length outside off, nudged to backward point for a single and that brings Butt on strike
Butt moves outside leg, Ishant sprays it well outside off. Wide.
edged to third man boundary as Praveen Kumar didn't pick the ball at all. It was fullish, just outside off, slashed off the outside edge to Praveen's left who stood there unable to sight the ball
backs to leg again and drives a full pitched delivery to long-off
Lovely crashing square drive. He moved outside leg, created room and square drove a full delivery on the off stump on a bent knee.
stays where he is and dabs a back-of-length delivery to third man
Butt tries to reprise Misbah's dab to third man but fails to connect
slows up the pace, turning past Misbah who goes, for what else but the slog sweep and fails to connect.
thunderous hit over long-off. Flighted outside off again and this time, Misbah waits for the ball to arrive before blasting it up and over long-off
full and outside leg, top edges his sweep to deep backward square leg region
moves well outside leg, Chawla serves it outside off, drags his drive to the on side
Biff. Blast. Boom. Batman comics time here. Couple of steps down the track and lofts it cleanly over wide long-on region.
and for variety edges this one through third man. He went for a big slash and got a profitable edge
wide full toss, Misbah reached out for it and connected with the toe end of the bat and Yuvraj fieds at point
cutting away from Misbah who runs it down to third man
full on off stump, tries to smash it down the ground.. the bowler takes the pace off the ball
fullish, flashed off the outer edge through point
pushes towards mid-off for a single
full delivery outside off stump and Misbah swings it to long-on boundary. Good bat speed on the down swing and the ball flies away
low dipping full toss on middle and leg, Misbah twists his body, gets his bottom-hand working over time and sends it to deep backward square leg boundary
short of length, outside off stump, flat-batted to long-off. Didn't time that well
slower one, full in length, driven to point
bouncer and Afrid ducks.
fuller one, driven to sweeper cover
full pitched delivery and driven hard but straight to long-off
slower one outside off, Misbah tries to cut but can't connect.
Low full toss, Misbah swings it straight to Rohit Sharma, standing near the ropes at long-on, who takes it the 'Australian style' .
full and outside off, slashed to fine third man
moves outside leg and mistimes a drive uppishly to covers where Praveen Kumar dives forward but can't reach it
again Praveen is the fielder, has a shy at the non-striker's end but Malik is home.
shuffles outside off, misses the waft across the line and was struck on the pad outside off stump
slower one and Afridi is through his shot early, no wood on leather and Dhoni gathers
low full toss, Afridi shapes to swing it over midwicket but edges it to third man
fullish, just short of the yorker length, outside off stump, Malik jabs a drive off the inside edge to left of Dhoni
The slog sweep has worked brilliantly for Pakistan tonight. The front leg was cleared and down came the bat in a hurry
another swing but not well timed and the ball rolls to deep midwicket
moves outside leg first before walking right across to the off side, Ishant remains calm and serves a full one on the off stump, flicked away for a single
low full toss, Afridi makes contact rather high on the bat and mistimes his lofted shot for  couple of runs to long-on
done in by the change of pace again. Outside off, the bat came down very early and it bounced awkwardly just in front of Dhoni who couldn't gather cleanly
yorker length delivery outside off stump, Malik moves outside leg, crouches to chop the ball through the slip region.
moves outside off, misses a paddle sweep and the ball rushes past the off stump to DHoni who underamred a throw at striker's end, missed and Ishant collected, turned around but held on to the ball
really full again, driven through covers for couple of runs

inn2.comm: Gambhir starts the chase with a fluent square drive. He leaned into the stroke and found the gap between point and covers
hits the deck short of length, on the middle and leg, and it runs off the pad as Gambhir hops to work it to leg side. THere must have been an inside edge
coming in towards middle and leg, off the length, clipped past square leg
fuller, on the middle and off, nipping back in, Sehwag is rooted at the crease and inside edges a drive to the on side.
short of length, straightens on the middle and off, worked to midwicket.
full, on that middle and off line, Sehwag is standing inside the crease, doesn't come forward and mistimes a drive to mid-on
hint of inswing but it slips down leg side and it runs off the pads to fine leg
slanting away from Sehwag who watches it sail into Akmal's gloves
beaten outside off stump, Angling away from Sehwag who has a lame poke at it.
closer to the off stump, again moving away with the angle, steered to backward point

Sohail Tanvir takes out Sehwag. Fullish, on the off and middle stump line, Sehwag shapes to drive through the on side, the bat face shuts early and the ball lobs off the leading edge to mid-off. Pakistan are over the moon. All fielders converge to celebrate the big wicket.
cutting away from Rohit who searches for the delivery outside off
length delivery outside off, steered to backward point
short of length, on the middle stump line, defended to the off side
fuller, just outside off, driven to Afridi at mid-off
lands on the leg stump line, moves towards middle and leg, Gambhir stays beside the line and drives to mid-on
Fullish, outside off stump, free flowing off drive past mid-off.
Blasted through the off side. charges down the track, moves outside leg and crashes a full delivery on the off stump through cover point.
length delivery outside off stump, pushed to point
length delivery moving away from Rohit who pushes at it, bat away from the body and squeezes it to off the outer edge to third man
beaten on the flirt. It straightened off a length outside off and Gambhir pushed with an open-face of the bat inside the line
And again. This time straightens from short of length and Gambhir  has a poke at it.
wide down the leg side and Akmal makes an acrobatic half-stop and the batsmen rush across for a bye as well
leans forward to wrist a length delivery on middle and leg to midwicket
fuller, just outside off stump, Rohit doesn't lean forward well, pushes at it with an open-face of the bat and the ball rolls towards backward point
not all that short at all and very close to the off stump but Gambhir goes back to force it through point. Good bat speed.
fuller and he rotates the strike with a push to left of mid-on
on a length, around off stump and defended to the off side
and again.
edged to third man boundary. Full, on the middle and off and curving away, Rohit tries to wrist it across the line and edges it past the first slip
similar line and Rohit plays with the full face of the bat in the V to mid-off
turns the strike over with a dab to third man.
short of length delivery moving from middle and leg towards off, punched back to the bowler

stifled shout for a catch down leg and Ashoka signals it as a wide. It was a length delivery and there was a noise. Was it the ball hitting the thigh pad or the bat hitting the thigh pad. Yousuf and Malik have a chat with the umpire
Rao Iftikhar makes a mess of a regulation stop at long leg. It was clipped to his right and he came around, swooped but missed it completely
on a length, angling away from Rohit who punches it off the back foot to covers
leans forward to punch a length delivery on the up to mid-off. Ashoka has a close look at the pitch, at the landing area
beaten on the drive. Rohit tried to drive on the up and the bat flashed inside the line of the length delivery angling across him.
on the middle and leg, turned to square leg
full in length, outside off stump, nonchalantly driven to sweeper cover
on a length, just outside off, holds its line, Rohit tries to punch drive on the up and gets an inside edge to the on side
backs to the leg side a touch even as he takes a couple of steps down the track and drives a length delivery inside out through extra cover.
gets close to the line of a good-length delivery and pushes it to the off side
works a length delivery from the off stump to square leg
just outside off, run down to third man for a single and Tanvir taps Gambhir on his helmet
fuller ,on the middle line, driven crisply to mid-on
just outside off stump and pushed to left of short extra cover
gets forward to drive on the up to short square point fielder
punches the length delivery coming into him to right of mid-on where Yousuf tries to stop it with his boot and misses. Tanvir is very disappointed.
on the hips and fended to the on side
fullish , on the off stump line and Gambhir wrists it from there through midwicket against the line and into the gap
fraction short of length and Rohit latches on to the length to pull it over midwicket.
fuller, on the middle, Rohit presses his front leg across to wrist it to deep square leg
on a length, slanted across, dabbed with soft hands and he gets a leading edge to the off side
works a length delivery to square leg
a tad slower, full in length. Rohit checks his drive and pushes it to left of short extra cover
Tanvir gets an extra over and he lands the first ball on a length on the off stump line, pushed to extra cover
short of length, on the middle and leg, Rohit stayed still and clipped it past square leg fielder.
fuller, curving in a touch, Rohit quickly takes out the front leg out of the way and jabs it bat and pad together to the on side
comes down the track, moves outside leg , Sohail remains calm and follows him with a short-of-length delivery that bounces a bit and Gambhir tries to dab it to the off side and misses
leans forward to square drive a fuller delivery to short square point that they have placed for him
super stop from Fawad Alam at point. Gambhir had laced a square drive and Alam went tumbling to his left to make the stop
Superb shot! on a length, on middle and leg, Gambhir walked down the track and smashed that over the midwicket boundary
back of a length, angling into the batsman, some width provided, pushed towards point for a single
pitched it short, Rohit tries a short-arm jab, takes the top edge and it flies straight into the hands of Nasir Jamshed at deep-backward square leg
good length, on leg and middle, jabbed to cover and batsmen take a quick single
what a confident shot off his first ball, on a length and wide outside off, slammed through covers.
on a length, on leg stump, Yusuf defends it
again on a length, outside off, pushed towards mid-off, and the batsmen scamper a single
stunning shot, length delivery is slammed straight back past the bowler
short of length, Yusuf pushes it to square leg
outside off, guided to third man
defended to the off side
steered to backward point, no run

He's gone! that's the wicket Pakistan wanted, banged in short, just a bit of width, Gambhir upper cuts it powerfully but is held at backward point by Nasir Jamshed, just a few yards in from the boundary
good length, but gives him room, good-looking drive through covers from Yusuf
tests him with the short ball, but strays down the leg, helped it on its way down to the fine leg boundary
outside off, pushed by Yusuf towards point
Gul oversteps and that's a free hit,  driven to mid-off
sends down a bouncer and Yusuf can't connect, terrific delivery on the free-hit
another length delivery, Yuvraj drives it to cover
shortish, on the legs, Yuvraj taps it towards short midwicket, a bit of a misfield, but batsmen decide against going for the run
lovely shot for little result, width offered and he drives it to short cover
sliding down leg, pushed to midwicket
driven to cover
short ball, on middle and leg, Yuvraj gets on the back foot and fends it back to the bowler
superb delivery, back of a length, and a hint of away movement, beats the batsman
and again, bit more bounce this time, and the batsman can't connect
excellent over so far, keeping it in the channel, good length and defended to the off
short ball, this time on middle and leg,short-arm pull off the front foot for four
short ball, Yusuf gets back and defends it confidently
fascinating battle on here, tests him with the bouncer again, slightly outside off, Yusuf thought about going for the pull but backed out at the last instant
short and poorly directed as well, that was on Yuvraj's pads and he dispatches it to the midwicket boundary
Yuvraj is looking good here, overpitched, wide outside off, driven forcefully but fielded at extra cover
back of a length, on middle, Yuvraj defends on the back foot
width offered, Yuvraj unleashes another powerful drive, a bit of a misfield at extra cover
closer to the off stump this time, again driven to extra cover
back of a length, on middle and leg, Yuvraj nearly played inside the line of that one, keeps it out but looked uncomfortable there
That was a poor start, short and very wide down leg
tries to sweep, edged onto his pads
huge appeal for leg-before, flighted and length delivery, Yuvraj goes for the sweep and is rapped on the pads, that might have pitched a bit outside leg
short of length, outside off and angling in, Yusuf pushes to cover
quick delivery, keeping it on Yuvraj's pads, he turns it away behind square
another big appeal, big step forward and hits him on the pad, but the umpire has given it as runs
down the leg, and thuds into his pads
Gone! he's holed out to midwicket, not the greatest of deliveries, back of a length on off stump, he could have smashed that anywhere, instead he hits it to Younis Khan
short of a length, on the off, defended watchfully
short of a length, angling away from the left-hander and he pushes it away to the off
that was another chance, pushed to mid-on, quick single taken, that was close and Yuvraj didn't even ground his bat
tossed up and driven to sweeper cover
on a length, turn and bounce, inside edged to the leg side
turned to short fine leg
overpitched outside off, driven to cover
massive appeal, Raina goes for the sweep, he too doesn't connect, but that looked to have pitched outside leg
Lovely shot, short on leg stump, he sends it over midwicket for another six
another short ball, but outside off this time, Yuvraj hits it towards backward point
short ball, on middle and off, worked away to mid-on
better delivery, keeping it tight and pitching on a good length, Raina pushes it to mid-off
overpitched on off, driven again to mid-off, batsmen scamper a single this time
fullish, well outside off, Yuvraj carves that through the covers, but can't beat the fielder in the deep
turns in from outside off, punched to long-off. "Well bowled Shahid Bhai," screams Akmal
clipped through midwicket for a single
goes back waits for the turn and turns it to fine leg
from round the stumps, lands it just outside off, jabbed off the front foot
full and outside leg, should have been put away but Raina misses it completely
leans forward to drive to long-off
and again, another single down to long-on
turns from just outside leg, worked to midwicket for a single
turns from well outside leg, turned to Yousuf at short fineleg
leans forward to defend a delivery that pitched outside leg stump and hits him on the pad
goes right back to a really full delivery and works it to square leg. Should have gone forward
on the middle stump line, defended down the track
floated full on the middle and leg, whipped through wide midwicket
overpitched outside off stump and Yuvraj goes down his knee to drill it to wide long-off boundary. "Koi baat nahi Koi bat nahi," says Akmal to Afridi( No worries)
tossed full on the leg and middle line, spun in a touch and Yuvraj misses the sweep shot and it would have hit the leg stump. Afridi shouts for another lbw but again turned down.
leans forward to push to the on side
rotates the strike with a drive
full and down the leg side and Yuvraj plays the vertical sweep really hard to the boundary
leans forward to drive to long-on for a single
spins in from outside leg stump, Yuvraj pushes it to the on side

full and outside leg stump - Malik has been landing his deliveries outside leg to the left-handed batsmen - Yuvraj leans forward to flick it through fine leg region well to the left of the short fine leg fielder
shifts his line to the middle, slow through the air and defended back down the track
again pitches it outside leg and Yuvraj sweeps it hard past the short fine-leg fielder
yet again turning from outside leg - he has five men on the off side - worked through midwicket for easy runs
outside leg, tickled to Afridi at short fine-legf
leans forward to drive to long-off
goes back to punch it to long-off
this time a single down to long-on
full, on the middle stump line, Raina works it past square leg
on the middle and leg, whipped to wide mid-on
long hop and Raina goes back to pull it to deep midwicket boundary wide of the fielder
another long hop  -  Malik is gifting boundaries  here - and Raina crashes this one to deep square leg boundary.

another shout for the lbw and again not given. It was full, on the middle and leg, spinning away and Raina tried to whip it across the line, missed and  to add to Pakistan' woes a run out chance is also missed.  Fawad Alam ran in from short third man and dived forward to throw at the stumps, missed and Akmal was not standing behind the stumps. btw yet another close shout for lbw.
lands outside leg stump, turns in to rap Yuvraj on the pad
sweeps a full delivery outside leg to long leg
goes back to turn it to fine leg

dropped by Fawad.  Yuvraj went back to punch a drive and it went off the edge slower than what Fawad anticipated and he didn't get in a good position and clanged it. It went chest-high and Fawad was actually thinking it would come really hard at him
leans forward to defend
leans forward to drive to long-on
goes back to cut to covers
quicker and flatter, just outside off but Yuvraj went back, allowed it to turn before cutting it through backward point
slower in the air, bit more air, full and on the middle, driven to long-off
goes back to a full delivery to punch to extra cover
again goes back to a full delivery that most batsmen would have gone forward and wrists it through midwicket
lunges forward to defend a delivery that landed on leg and middle line
fuller, pitches outside leg, Yuvraj tries to flick across the line, against the turn and gets an edge to right of short third man
driven through extra cover for couple of runs and that's his fifty
full and outside the leg stump
loopy flighted delivery on the off stump, hit back to the bowler
leans across to whip a full delivery to wide long-on
steps down the track and Fawad hurls it quicker and also, drags back the length, squeezed to backward point
done in by a full toss outside leg! Raina, who was lucky to survive a close lbw decision earlier, top edged his sweep to deep square leg where Afridi ran in to take a lunging catch.
goes back to punch it back to Afridi
leans forward to turn a full delivery past square leg
cut to sweeper cover for a single
quicker. flatter and shorter, swatted to square leg
leans forward to mistime drive back to bowler
goes right back to jab a quick delivery to the leg side
leans forward to drive a full delivery to long-on
on the leg stump line, turning in, pushed back to the bowler
again patted back to the bowler.
slower through the air, outside off stump, and Dhoni mistimes yet another drive back to the bowler
rotates the strike with a wristy stroke to deep square leg
lands on the middle and leg, turns, Dhoni pushes it to the off side, wants a run and wisely sent back.
takes out the front leg from the line and drives inside-out to left of long-off where Tanvir makes a fine diving stop
goes back to work to midwicket

And finally Afridi gets a favorable nod from umpire Nadir Shah. It was the slider that skidded across Yuvraj after landing on back of length on the off and middle line, Yuvraj shaped to pull and got a thin bottom edge through to Akmal. Yuvraj too was lucky to survive couple of close lbw decisions.
landed outside leg stump and hits Irfan on the pad
drills a full delivery to long-off
short, flat, worked to deep midwicket for a single
short again, on the middle stump, Dhoni backs away to the leg side to cut to covers
stays on the leg stump line to push a shortish delivery to long-off
fuller, turning into Irfan who turns to left of midwicket
fuller and Dhoni was late in leaning forward - he might have thought another short of length delivery was coming in-  and pushes it to the off side
defended to the on side
on the middle and leg, paddled to the on side
lands on a length on middle and length ,skids on to middle, Irfan goes back to drive back to Afridi
leans forward to drive to long-off
full and sliding down leg side, Akmal can't get across in time and neither could Yousuf, the short fine-leg fielder
just outside off stump, going on straight, left alone
shout for lbw but he was struck just outside off stump. He lunged across and got just outside the line even as the ball skid in
low full toss, swatted to long-off
short ball and pulled to deep backward square-leg boundary
leans forward to push with the turn to covers
outside off stump, full in length, cut to deep backward point
another short and flat delivery, forced off the back foot to long-off
leans forward to tap a full delivery to midwicket
on a yorker length, dug out by Dhoni
on the legs, Dhoni goes back to tickle it behind square leg
tries to sweep but doesn't make proper contact
driven to long-off
on the leg and middle, worked through the on side for a single
full and outside off stump, Irfan misses a cover drive
leans forward to defend a length delivery to covers
fullish, driven straight to covers
short of length and swatted to deep square leg
length delivery coming in towards off stump and Dhoni gets back to jab it to the off side
outside off stump, dabbed to third man
on the off stump, skidding on straight, cut to point
a tad shorter and cut to covers
on the middle, Dhoni takes care not to press his front leg across and pushes to left of cover fielder
swung over deep square leg. The falling sweep shot. He came down and swung it high and over and fell over his back side in the process
comes down the track and has a heave but inside edges on to the pad
short, angling outside off, pulled to deep square leg, straight to the fielder
over-steps this time, full and outside off, cracked towards deep point, they get a single and there's a free-hit coming up
good-length ball, slightly slower, Irfan tries to swing towards midwicket but only manages an inside edge back to the keeper, yet another free hit that goes abegging
carved over point but there's a man in the deep
yorker this time, outside off, digs it out towards mid-off for a quick one
full and angling away from the left-hander, drives past extra-cover and they hurry a couple
on the legs, turned to deep backward square leg and take two more
short of length and swat-pulled over midwicket into the gap between deep midwicket and long-on
short of length, just outside off stump, squeezed off the outer edge past the diving Akmal. partly edged, partly steered
length delivery outside off stump, forced to deep point
ful toss, just below waist-high, edged to left of Akmal, it bounces before him and he doesn't collect it cleanly
walks down the track and across, whips a full delivery through midwicket
fullish, on the middle and leg, driven to mid-on
from round the stumps, full and on the middle and leg, flicked straight to short fine leg. A foot to left or right of the fielder would have cost TAnvir a boundary
shifts his line to outside off, comes in with the angle, punched to extra cover
full on the middle, Dhoni walks across to whip it through midwicket. He would keep doing that, a slight shuffle to work with the angle to the on side
on the off stump, worked to the on side but can't beat the midwicket fielder this time
slower one, outside off stump, Dhoni beaten on the square drive
full toss coming in to the middle stump, pushed to long-on for a single.
cuts in off a length from just outside off stump, worked to midwicket
swing and a miss. Just outside off stump, Irfan tried to heave it over midwicket
low full toss outside off and Irfan misses an opportunity there, swing and a miss
And again! Irfan has missed another full toss outside off. Dhoni remains still at the non-striker's end; he doesn't want to put any pressure on his team-mate.
off cutter around off stump, cut past covers. Akmal is shouting his lungs out: C'mon boys or Shabash ...
leans forward to drive a length delivery back to the bowler. Just two runs in this over.
another full toss, on the leg stump line, turned to midwicket for a quick single, Misbah fired in a direct hit but Dhoni was home
slower one, full, driven to extra cover
on the pads, Irfan can't put bat to ball and it bobs off the pad to the off side
low full toss spearing into middle stump line, squeezed to backward point
Irfan gets a boundary; He picked the slower one to pull it to deep square leg boundary
length delivery on the off stump, Irfan wanted to pull it through midwicket but edges it past the bowler for a single
Another wicket goes down. Irfan pulls a short-of-length delivery to midwicket. No power or timing there and it just lobbed to the fielder.
tight line and length - on the off stump off a good length, punched to long-off for a single.
short of length, coming in to PK who hops and works it to midwicket for a quick single. Misbah with the throw but he misses and PK would have been out had it hit
forces a low full toss on the off stump one bounce to long-off
full pitched, driven powerfully but straight to long-off
on the middle and leg, Dhoni keeps the strike with a push down to long-on
walks to outside off stumps, edges an intended slog past square leg
comes in to cramp Praveen who dabs it to the on side for a single
full toss from wide of the crease, Dhoni makes contact with the top half of the bat and will only get a single to long-off
just short of the blockhole, outside off and Praveen Kumar can't connect with his drive. Just three runs so far in this over
full again on the off stump, driven to deep cover for a single. Sohail is keeping things very tight here. Good stuff from him.

dropped by Gul at long-off. Dhoni walked down the track, Tanvir hurled it full and outside off and Dhoni drove it to left of Gul who couldn't hold on to it.  Pakistan are still in the driver's seat but how costly is that going to be?
fullish, just outside off stump, the yorker length, Praveen tries to chop it to third man but can't connect. Dhoni walks across to have a chat
full and straight, mistimes a drive to long-on. Praveen is standing still on the leg stump line and trying to drive hard but has been unable to connect cleanly
low dipping full toss, he went for a yorker, hit straight to long-off
trapped in front. He thrust his front foot across and tried to paddle a low full toss on the leg stump line. It would have hit the leg stump.
lovely probing delivery rushing past the outside edge. Fab bowling from Pakistan at the death.
really full again, nagging length and Piyush can only dig it out to the off side.
full toss just below waist-high, swung to deep square leg region.
fullish, on the middle and leg line, Dhoni took out the front leg away from the line and whipped it to wide long-on region

on a length and that allows Dhoni to get under the ball and send it soaring over long-on. Tanvir has been repeatedly hitting the yorker length and he just got off the length this time and was punished.

gets this one fuller, driven to right of long-off, they come back for the second run, the throw comes chest-high to Tanvir who breaks the stumps and Piyush just about manages to drag back the crease in time. The bails weren't completely dislodged by the time the bat came in. Dhoni reached his fifty with those couple of runs
just outside off stump, almost yorker-length again, Dhoni crouches to chop it past Akmal and runs hard to come back for the 2nd run
lunges forward to take the ball on the full and drives to long-off for a single
Dhoni walked across the stumps and tried to paddle a full delivery past short fineleg missed and was struck on the pad just outside off stump
Piyush moves outside leg and Gul follows him with a yorker on his boots and they get across for leg bye
Dhoni gets a boundary. A low full toss and outside off and Dhoni hit it inside out to wide long-off boundary
full pitched around the off stump and Dhoni unfurls his special bottom-handed twirl and the ball raced along the turf but straight to long-off. Dhoni has a chat with Chawla

cleaned him up with a yorker. Gul has been bowling superbly at the death and continues to be reward for his accurate length. The bat couldn't come down in time and the death rattle for Chawla would have been delightful to Gul's ears. Nasim Ashraf is up on his feet, celebrating the wicket.
goes for the yorker, ends up as a low full toss, defended back to Gul.
one-handed six over deep square leg boundary. He charged down, Afridi hurled it short and fast and Dhoni pulled it away

another swing and this time he holes out to sweeper cover. Game over. Pakistan win the series. Malik rushes across and jumps at Afridi. They all converge. Now both teams shake hands with each other. Super win for Pakistan. They rebounded well after a big loss in the earlier game to win when it mattered. The Kitply cup is in the bag.
